    <p>The National Palace of Culture was built in 1981, to serve as a conference and exhibition center for various events.
      The vast exhibition spaces, numerous halls, and spectacular view from the spacious balconies, contribute to its cult status.</p>

    <p>The park around NDK is known as one of the hot spots for youngsters (and not only) and is just few minutes walk from one of Sofia's vibrant pedestrian streets - Vitosha.</p>

    <p>There is a metro station, conveniently located right at the venue entrance. </p>

